#### Package parameters

The following package parameter can be set:

* `/installPath:` specify a custom extract location as a full path - defaults to the 'C:\ProgramData\chocolatey\lib\exiftoolgui\tools' folder.
exiftoolgui save GUI settings on the same folder.
This parameter is for non admin privilege users.

```PowerShell
choco install exiftoolgui --params="'/installPath:C:\Users\username\Downloads\exiftoolgui'"
```

The exiftoolgui folder in a custom location will not get uninstalled automatically by this package. Please remove exiftoolgui manually after choco uninstall exiftoolgui.</description>
